    desc="Mana Type: Lava"
    status="DRAFT"
><>

<title>Lava Mana<>

<content>
    <section> Introduction <>
        <p>Lava mana is a type of mana which comes from molten rock. It is thick and viscous and can be extremely
        deadly when used as a weapon.<>
        <p>Lava mana has an affinity with <a t="#mana_*_fire">#<> and <a t="#mana_*_stone">#<>.<>

    <section> Caster Types <>
        <heading level="1">Lava Manipulator<>
        <p>Lava <a t="#mana_*_manipulators">manipulators<> throw about molten lava to burn their enemies and reduce
        them to nothing.<>

        <heading level="1">Lava Armorers<>
        <p>Lava <a t="#mana_*_armorers">armorers<> coat themselves in thick layers of molten rock which is very strong
        at deflecting attacks, but can also be used to great effect when hitting enemies.<>

        <heading level="1">Lava Animators<>
        <p>Lava <a t="#mana_*_animators">animators<> create lava elementals which are ozzing and melting constructions
        of lava which move slowly but can inflict severe damage to foes.<>

        <heading level="1">Lava Item Wielders<>
        <p>Lava <a t="#mana_*_itemWielders">item wielders<> wield items that emit lava on use.
        Examples include lava swords and lava drops.<>
<>
